title: Title - Cadence of Hyrule Soundtrack
description:
Join the Nintendo Music Channel Discord! http://discord.gg/tMnA9cm

Play as Link, or Princess Zelda as you move to the beat and try to defeat an evil menace disrupting Hyrule. Cadence of Hyrule: Crypt of the Necrodancer ft. The Legend of Zelda is out now only on the Nintendo Switch!

#CadenceOfHyrule #TheLegendOfZelda #Nintendo
